<b>Boba Shop POS</b>

    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    CashierApp
    Main cashier application for handling food orders and menu items.
    CashierUI
    CashierUI provids an interface for cashiers to proces orders.
    DatabaseManager
    DatabaseManager handles database connections and provides methods for data access.
    Employee
    Employee model class representing employees in the boba shop.
    Inventory
    Inventory model class representing inventory items in the boba shop.
    LandingPage
    Landing page for the Boba Shop POS System.
    Main
    Main entry point for the Boba Shop POS System Displays landing page with Manager/Cashier options
    ManagerUI
    Manager UI for managing menu, inventory, employees, and reports.
    MenuItem
    MenuItem model class representing a menu item in the boba shop.
    MockDataProvider
    MockDataProvider provides mock data for testing and development purposes.
    Order
    Order model class representing customer orders in the boba shop.
    OrderItem
    OrderItem model class representing individual items within an order.
